summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 3001, for the improvement of the following described property in Denny & Hoyt's Addition; Lots 13 to 21 inclusive, Block 53; Lots 13 to 24 inclusive, Block 54; Lots 10 to 24 inclusive, Block 55; Lots 11 to 24 inclusive, Block 57; Lots 11 to 24 inclusive, Block 58; Lots 1 to 20 inclusive, Block 67; Lots 1 to 24 inclusive, Block 68; Lots 1 to 17 inclusive, Block 69; Lots 1 to 10 inclusive, Block 70; all in the City of Seattle, known as Denny & Hoyt's Sanitary Fill No. 1; under Ordinance No. 36154 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
